title: World of Warcraft: Cataclysm 5.4.1 Mac
description:
World of Warcraft: Cataclysm
Version: 5.4.1
Language: English (enGB)

Full World of Warcraft Cataclysm client. Includes the original game and all expansions up to Cataclysm. Additional game data will download automatically as you play. Downloading this file skips the game installation. All you have to do is unzip, drag to applications, and play.
